07/02/2003
BUJANOVAC, Serbia-Montenegro -- Macedonian Defence Minister Vlado Buckovski met Thursday (6 February) with Belgrade's co-ordinator for Kosovo, Nebojsa Covic, in Bujanovac. They discussed bilateral co-operation in safeguarding the common border. Afterwards, Buckovski headed to Tetovo to discuss with local authorities an army initiative for economic assistance to the region. (Makfax, MIA - 07/02/03)
